Martins mapping language:

mapping SVCL dsl.ServiceCall
  4-18: CustomerName
  19-23: CustomerID
  24-27 : CallTypeCode
  28-35 : DateOfCallString

mapping  USGE dsl.Usage
  4-8 : CustomerID
  9-22: CustomerName
  30-30: Cycle
  31-36: ReadDate


